Develop thematic data

.dominantCondition <- function(i, var) {
  
  i <- i[i$compkind != 'Miscellaneous area', ]
  if(nrow(i) < 1) {
    return(NULL)
  }
  
  fm <- as.formula(sprintf("comppct_r ~ %s", var))
  a <- aggregate(fm, data = i, FUN = sum, na.rm = TRUE)
  
  idx <- order(a[['comppct_r']], decreasing = TRUE)[1]
  
  res <- data.frame(
    mukey = i$mukey[1],
    v = a[[var]][idx]
  )
  names(res) <- c('mukey', var)
  
  return(res)
}

.dominantValue <- function(i, var) {
 
  i <- i[i$compkind != 'Miscellaneous area', ]
  if(nrow(i) < 1) {
    return(NULL)
  }
  
  
  idx <- order(i[['comppct_r']], decreasing = TRUE)[1]
  
  res <- data.frame(
    mukey = i$mukey[1],
    v = i[[var]][idx]
  )
  
  names(res) <- c('mukey', var)
  
  return(res)
  
}



co.taxpartsize <- do.call('rbind',
        lapply(
          split(rss.co, rss.co$mukey), 
          .dominantCondition, var = 'taxpartsize'
        )
)
